 ('1', '32', 'en_us', 'List Item\r\nSubhead', '<p>This component is very similar to the \"Two Column Arrow List\" component. However, in wider viewports, this component will take up the whole width of the content area instead of being split into two columns. You might want to use this component instead if your content for each list items is longer, or you have a smaller amount of items to list.</p>', 'Optional Button', '#', 'arrow-right', '2016-08-05 17:34:46', '2016-08-19 18:50:03', '6c95ab94-ec24-4a6d-917c-9bb64650ea3d'),
 ('2', '33', 'en_us', 'Another List \r\nItem Subhead', '<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Etiam eleifend vestibulum odio vitae elementum. Morbi faucibus odio tincidunt porttitor tincidunt. Nam aliquet, urna ut egestas pretium, diam erat ultricies leo, quis molestie nibh sem vel lorem. </p>\n\n<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Etiam eleifend vestibulum odio vitae elementum. Morbi faucibus odio tincidunt porttitor tincidunt. Nam aliquet, urna ut egestas pretium, diam erat ultricies leo, quis molestie nibh sem vel lorem. <br /></p>', '', '', 'arrow-right', '2016-08-05 17:34:46', '2016-08-19 18:50:03', '23e739c6-beae-4ac6-80f1-e6f92d6f2644'),
 ('3', '610', 'en_us', 'Digital GTM Strategy', '<p>Without a vision on how digital platforms, tools, and capabilities fit into your GTM strategy, business opportunity can pass you by. We can help you craft a digitally-savvy and customer-focused business model powered by modern techniques and solid digital fundamentals.<br /></p>', '', '', 'arrow-right', '2016-08-18 19:52:19', '2016-08-19 18:31:20', '43745008-6c64-4a20-927e-68d2c809ea6f'),
 ('4', '611', 'en_us', 'Connected Sales & Marketing', '<p>Lead generation without connecting sales and marketing efforts via lead nurturing is really only half of the job. We can help you bridge the gaps between departments, nurture prospects, and ready your Sales, Tele, and Partner teams.</p>', '', '', 'arrow-right', '2016-08-18 19:52:19', '2016-08-19 18:31:20', 'c18d81b5-d3dc-4094-a3f7-01e602e901a4'),
 ('5', '612', 'en_us', 'Campaigns, Content, & Consumer', '<p>Companies who don’t plan for multi-touch, multi-platform buying processes are playing roulette with their marketing efforts. With intelligent campaigns and a long-term view of customer lifecycles, we’ll partner with you to create meaningful value for your buyers<br /></p>', '', '', 'arrow-right', '2016-08-18 19:52:19', '2016-08-19 18:31:20', '735400e9-4625-4652-837a-6d9766a96421'),
 ('6', '613', 'en_us', 'Integrated Digital Experiences', '<p>Customers expect streamlined, consistent multi-platform experiences…and for you to know their preferences and history without having to ask. We can help you design and develop truly integrated experiences that will meet the expectations of your buyers.</p>', '', '', 'arrow-right', '2016-08-18 19:52:19', '2016-08-19 18:31:20', '834c4396-09c2-4956-b844-87a0e767c37e'),
 ('7', '617', 'en_us', 'Data-Powered Customer Insight', '<p><em>“I know my business and I know my customers, but I need insight that goes beyond intuition.”</em> </p>\n\n<p>\n  There’s lots of talk about big data these days. But, more often than not, it’s the critical smaller subsets that make a difference for your business. Using modern data science and insight mining techniques, we’ll help you extract value from your customer data and drive improved business outcomes.</p>', '', '', 'arrow-right', '2016-08-19 00:20:15', '2016-08-19 00:22:54', '4aace2f6-93c6-4a44-9011-dd3fff13d679'),
 ('8', '618', 'en_us', 'Modern Channel Models', '<p><em>“The needs of our channel partners don’t always align with the needs of our customers.”</em></p>\n\n<p>How you distribute your products evolves constantly. With mobile commerce, cloud commerce and virtual storefronts, creating scale and driving growth have never been more achievable. Or complex. We have deep-rooted experience in traditional, digital, cloud, and mobile channels. We’ll help you assess your distribution options and streamline digital commerce strategies.</p>', '', '', 'arrow-right', '2016-08-19 00:20:15', '2016-08-19 00:22:54', '7321737d-67cb-46ef-a0f6-d738c39e7447'),
 ('9', '619', 'en_us', 'Customer Journeys & Personas', '<p><em>“We need to add value for my customers without sacrificing margin.”</em></p>\n\n<p>Customers go on a “journey” when making buying decisions. Many companies know this, but not many actively help buyers along the way. They should: a striking number of buyers prefer to buy from companies that engage with them throughout their journey. We understand customer needs along the path to purchase and will help you engage with them in a value exchange that turns leads into sales</p>', '', '', 'arrow-right', '2016-08-19 00:20:15', '2016-08-19 00:22:54', 'befafdd6-cd6a-425b-90f9-0275ec77f5e3');
